","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, L:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a twisted part"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a horn:"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a twisted internodal portion"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a horn: (L:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any prominence"},{"kind":"text","text":"in a horn, and in a mountain, (S, L, K,) &c.: (S, L:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a prominent and curved part"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a mountain: (T:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a projecting portion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ledge,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a mountain,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"resembling a wing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, L, K:) pl. (of the former word, S)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHoyaAdN","text_ar":"اَحْيَادٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[a pl. of pauc.] and (of both words, S)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuyuwdN","text_ar":"حُيُودٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and (of the latter, S)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiyadN","text_ar":"حِيَدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K:) the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Huyuwd","text_ar":"حُيُود"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a camel are such parts as the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hips,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"haunches,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thighs."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) You say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jabalN *uw HuyuwdK","text_ar":"جَبَلٌ ذُو حُيُودٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHoyaAdK","text_ar":"اَحْيَادٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A mountain having projecting edges in its lower parts,"},{"kind":"text","text":"not in its upper parts. (S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaEadotu","text_ar":"قَعَدْتُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taHota Hayodi Aljabali","text_ar":"تَحْتَ حَيْدِ الجَبَلِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I sat beneath the part of the mountain that projected like a wing."},{"kind":"text"